					<h3 class="paia__headingH3 headingH3--paia">3.1 <span>Request Procedure</span></h3>
					<p class="paia__paragraph paragraph paragraph--legalClause">
						To request access to a record, please send a written request to the Information Officer using <strong>Form C</strong> (available on the Information Regulator’s website). Your
						request must include:
					</p>
					<ul class="paia__list">
						<li class="paia__paragraph paragraph paragraph--legalClause">A clear description of the record(s) sought</li>
						<li class="paia__paragraph paragraph paragraph--legalClause">The preferred form of access (e.g., electronic, printed)</li>
						<li class="paia__paragraph paragraph paragraph--legalClause">Proof of identity (if requested)</li>
					</ul>
				</section>
				<section class="paia__subsection">
					<h3 class="paia__headingH3 headingH3--paia">3.2 <span>Grounds for Refusal</span></h3>
					<p class="paia__paragraph paragraph paragraph--legalClause">Access to certain records may be refused under the following conditions:</p>
					<ul class="paia__list">
						<li class="paia__paragraph paragraph paragraph--legalClause">Protection of third-party privacy or confidentiality</li>
						<li class="paia__paragraph paragraph paragraph--legalClause">Protection of commercial information</li>
						<li class="paia__paragraph paragraph paragraph--legalClause">Unreasonable burden on resources or repeated excessive requests</li>
					</ul>
				</section>
			</section>
